---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Imprint – Norway Card Advisor" description="Legal information and contact details for Norway Card Advisor.">
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Imprint</h1>
    <p class="mb-4">This imprint is provided in accordance with §5 TMG (German Telemedia Act) and the Norwegian E‑commerce Act.</p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Site Operator</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">Norway Card Advisor<br />
    Representative: [Your Name]<br />
    Oebisfelde, Saxony‑Anhalt, Germany</p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Contact</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">Email: <a href="mailto:info@example.com" class="text-accent underline">info@example.com</a><br />
    Phone: +49 000 000 0000 (placeholder)</p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Responsible for Content</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">[Your Name]<br />
    Address as above.</p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">EU Dispute Resolution</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">The European Commission provides a platform for online dispute resolution (ODR) which you can access at <a href="https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr" class="text-accent underline">https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr</a>. We are neither obliged nor willing to participate in a dispute settlement procedure before a consumer arbitration board.</p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>The information provided on this website has been compiled with utmost care. However, we do not guarantee its completeness or accuracy. Links to external websites are beyond our control; we do not accept any responsibility for their content.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>